title: New Beginnings are right around the corner ♥ LOCK this price in now!
posting_body: ['Step Into The Sinclair!', 'Step into The Sinclair: The stuff that life is made of.', 'Our newly built vintage chic community in Port Orchard presents 1, 2 & 3 bedroom homes.', 'Each private apartment provides well-organized space and storage options along with immaculate, stylish appliances and designer fixtures and lighting.', 'Relax outside on your private deck or patio with community, pool and wooded views.', 'Upgrade features available including plank flooring and advanced connectivity.', 'Experience our club house, outdoor grills, playgrounds, fitness center and convenient car detailing area.', 'Don’t wait, Contact The Sinclair today!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 96', 'OR Text', '96', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 733 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Dishwasher', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Internet/Cable Ready', '- Extra Storage', '- Full Size Washer/Dryer in Home', '- Efficient Appliances', 'Community Amenities', '- Seasonal Heated Pool', '- Business Center', '- Pet Friendly', '- Playground', '- 24/7 Fitness Center', '- Valet Trash Service', '- Covered Carports', '- Secured Garages', '- Recycling', '- Off Street Parking', '- Walking Trails', '- EV Charging Stations', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- High Speed Internet', '- On-Site Management', '- Resident Lounge', '- Amazon Lockers', '- Car Detailing Area', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats & Dogs allowed.', '2 pets per household.', 'One-time $600 non-refundable pet fee & additional $200 for 2nd pet.', 'Pet rent is $25 a month and $45 monthly for two', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5x rent to gross income ratio (household)', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 8:00AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday-Sunday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'The Sinclair', '414 SW Hayworth DR, Port Orchard, WA, 98367', 'aYMdxO3BHiPk']
